{"Id":486,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-mazhonggang","Author":"Ma Zhong Gang","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://alquran.cloud/api","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":95,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以无花果和橄榄果发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":95,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"以西奈山发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":95,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"以这座平安的城市[麦加]发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":95,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"我确已创造人于最完美的形态中，"},{"SurahNumber":95,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"然后，我又把他贬降成最卑贱的，"},{"SurahNumber":95,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"唯信仰并行善者例外，他们[信仰并行善者]将获得永恒的报酬[乐园]。"},{"SurahNumber":95,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"此后，什么[谁]使你[不信仰者]否认审判日呢？"},{"SurahNumber":95,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"难道安拉不是最好的审判者吗？"}]}